        <scopecontent>
          <p>The National Organization for Women (NOW) (1977-1986, .9 linear feet) series documents Hays-Hamilton's involvement with NOW at the local (Midland), state (Michigan), regional (Great Lakes) and national levels. Examples of the type of material found in this series are bylaws, minutes and correspondence. The majority of the series relates to the activities of the Michigan Conference of NOW when she was president. The Michigan Conference of NOW maintained no state office so each officer kept her own records. The researcher is directed to the records of the Michigan Conference of the National Organization for Women (call no. 85326 Bj 2) and the papers of Monica Smiley (call no. 85377 Aa 2) and Marian McCracken (call no. 9643 Aa 2) for more information on the Michigan Conference of NOW.</p>
